divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking several pictures, so took several in succession, because the subject was interesting to me. Anyway, I was walking down Highway 35 about 3 miles away from Trempealeau, WI, USA. So today I used my camera for something else and looked over the pictures one by one on my computer that I had taken just a couple days before. ( Trempealeau Mountain has been considered sacred to the ancient people around here.) It is the mountain you see in the pictures. I did not notice any such object until I looked at the pictures on my computer. I thought that maybe it could be a leaf blowing by, however the shapes seemed quite odd to me and I thought that maybe you all could look at these and tell me what you thought. There was alot of energy coming in with the storm, but I don't remember a lot of wind at this time, and the other pictures that I took do not show any wind either. What do you all think? I am sending pictures of all 3 pictures, which have the same exact time on all of them (I think the camera says A.M., but it should say P.M. as the pictures were taken in the afternoon.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Trempealeau
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: I was taking pictures of a storm but when I looked at them today, there were 3 unusual objects in only one of the pictures! The objects were not in the other 2 pictures taked at the same time...
